articles.author: Helen Regan
articles.title: Australian backpacker dies as countries warn of suspected methanol poisonings in Laos - CNN
articles.description: An Australian teenager has died and another is fighting for her life after drinking suspected tainted alcohol in Laos, as a growing list of countries warned of multiple poisonings linked to a tourist town in the Southeast Asian country.
